title: Final Burn Legends additional 1.13 roms + FBL 1.13
description:
Additional 1.13 roms for FBL 1.13:




This is another update to NES6502's Final Burn Legends.

Final Burn Legends is a port of Final Burn Alpha 2.99.07 to the Xbox. It also includes parts of FBA-XXX Pro 1.29. And some of the latest FBA code over 2700 games are supported.


Final burn Legends v1.13 whats New:



Added support for the following games

B-Rap-Boys 
B-Rap-Boys Special Versions
Fujiyama Buster
Knights Of Valor Superheroes Plus
Shogun Warriors
The Killing Blade Plus

PGM bugfixes

Fixed the graphical bug in The Gladiator Road Of The Sword
Fixed the missing graphics in SVG Spectral Vs Generation
Fixed the dip switches And the Fake Regions so they now save in...
Puzzli 2
puzzli 2 super 
The Gladiator Road Of The Sword
SVG Spectral Vs Generation


Data East Core Massive Update
